# ADMIN — PROJECT MANAGEMENT
###############################################################################

### List All Projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### List Projects with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/projects?status=pending&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

