Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Insufficient documentation provided."
}

---

### Toggle Featured Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/projects/{{projectId}}/featured
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isFeatured": true
}

